			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				There seems to be some MAJOR confusion on the trivials for FINE PLATE.  For starters there are three differents types.  Fine,Field and Full plate.  The skill level listed above 175+ is not for Fine plate.  Fine plate collars trivial at 182.  I am making them at level 150.  Full plate is what is list above.  I do not know the trivials for field plate yet.  Just thought you should not this information.  Thanks<BR>
<BR>
JBJones<BR>
20 season on Vazealle<BR>
lvl 150 Blacksmith
